### FFI::Raw Implementation ###

$ perl wuserver.pl &
$ time perl wuclient.pl
Collecting updates from weather station...
Average temperature for zipcode '10001 ' was 21F

real    1m22.818s
user    0m0.070s
sys     0m0.023s


